<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 16:08:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>如果以色列军队入侵拉法，那里避难的超过150万巴勒斯坦人将何去何从？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-israel-invades-rafah-what-will-be-of-over-1-5m-palestinians-who-take-shelter-there/0000018d-9360-d443-a19f-fff113ba0000</link><description>以色列对拉法的入侵将导致近百万巴勒斯坦平民惊慌失措地大规模逃往大约本古里安机场大小的指定安全区。目前尚不清楚以色列国防军计划如何将其与国际法院的命令相协调，即以色列必须采取一切措施避免种族灭绝行为</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 15:40:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-israel-invades-rafah-what-will-be-of-over-1-5m-palestinians-who-take-shelter-there/0000018d-9360-d443-a19f-fff113ba0000</guid></item><item><title>穆迪致以色列：是政府，笨蛋！</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/moodys-to-israel-its-the-government-stupid/0000018d-92ee-d9cc-a5cd-f7fe76460000</link><description>为了保住权力，内塔尼亚胡不顾一切地支持以色列的宗教法西斯分子，并坚持敬畏上帝的经济政策。结果是以色列有史以来首次信用评级被下调</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 13:13:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/moodys-to-israel-its-the-government-stupid/0000018d-92ee-d9cc-a5cd-f7fe76460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境警察杀害了一名 4 岁巴勒斯坦女孩，10 天后才归还她的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-cops-killed-a-4-year-old-palestinian-girl-then-took-10-days-to-return-her-body/0000018d-90dd-d443-a19f-fcdd3cf20000</link><description>边境警察向一辆试图闯过检查站的车辆不分青红皂白地开枪，还向一辆载着一名母亲和她的孩子的出租车发射了 32 发子弹。其中一名小女孩被枪杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 03:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-cops-killed-a-4-year-old-palestinian-girl-then-took-10-days-to-return-her-body/0000018d-90dd-d443-a19f-fcdd3cf20000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩报道：两名真主党成员和叙利亚公民在以色列袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israels-economy-is-strong-credit-downgrade-is-only-due-to-war/0000018d-90d4-d57f-a1ef-b8dce9aa0000</link><description>加沙报道：以色列国防军在拉法杀死了哈马斯警察情报局长和另外两人 ■ 以色列国防军表示，以色列北部响起的数十个空中渗透警报是误报 ■ 叙利亚人权观察组织称，大马士革附近的以色列空袭造成三人死亡 ■ 穆迪下调以色列信用评级首次</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 03:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israels-economy-is-strong-credit-downgrade-is-only-due-to-war/0000018d-90d4-d57f-a1ef-b8dce9aa0000</guid></item><item><title>“抗议结束战争，母亲结束战争。”更多的以色列人应该呼吁结束这种疯狂行为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/protests-end-wars-moms-end-wars-more-israelis-should-call-for-an-end-to-this-madness/0000018d-9052-d443-a19f-fcd3789c0000</link><description>以色列单口喜剧演员诺姆·舒斯特-埃利亚西在阿拉伯世界也颇有名气，他呼吁人们不要再忽视对方的悲伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 02:31:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/protests-end-wars-moms-end-wars-more-israelis-should-call-for-an-end-to-this-madness/0000018d-9052-d443-a19f-fcd3789c0000</guid></item><item><title>“我的人头要出价”：数百名普通以色列人因血仇而躲藏起来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theres-a-price-on-my-head-these-ordinary-israelis-are-in-hiding-due-to-blood-feuds/0000018d-8fb8-d9cc-a5cd-ffba41150000</link><description>他们是守法的以色列阿拉伯公民——医生、律师、教师——由于涉及家人的致命争斗，他们无法离开罗德城的家</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 00:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theres-a-price-on-my-head-these-ordinary-israelis-are-in-hiding-due-to-blood-feuds/0000018d-8fb8-d9cc-a5cd-ffba41150000</guid></item><item><title>穆迪历史上首次下调以色列信用评级，展望下调至“负面”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/moodys-downgrades-israels-credit-rating-for-first-time-in-countrys-history/0000018d-8eb1-d57f-a1ef-bebde2450000</link><description>穆迪决定不仅降低以色列的信用评级，而且还下调其信用前景，这让耶路撒冷的官员感到意外。虽然现在确定此举的财务影响还为时过早，但这对以色列的国际形象造成了严重打击</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 21:46:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/moodys-downgrades-israels-credit-rating-for-first-time-in-countrys-history/0000018d-8eb1-d57f-a1ef-bebde2450000</guid></item><item><title>2016年逃往加沙的以色列贝都因人被捕，被指控加入哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bedouin-who-fled-to-gaza-in-2016-arrested-accused-of-joining-hamas/0000018d-8f14-d57f-a1ef-bf1c2a2c0000</link><description>Juma Ibrahim Abu-Ganima 在 12 月试图返回以色列后被拘留。他被指控向哈马斯提供有关以色列南部以色列国防军基地的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 18:59:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bedouin-who-fled-to-gaza-in-2016-arrested-accused-of-joining-hamas/0000018d-8f14-d57f-a1ef-bf1c2a2c0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 126 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-126/0000018d-8ea2-d57f-a1ef-bebebf870000</link><description>据报道，美国高级情报官员估计只有三分之一的加沙哈马斯战士被杀 ■ 内塔尼亚胡命令国防机构提出撤离拉法的计划 ■ 美国国务院称以色列在拉法的行动“将是一场灾难” ■ 红新月会：以色列军队袭击了阿尔及尔- 汗尤尼斯的阿迈勒医院 ■ 以色列国防军：上个月被宣布死亡的以色列人质很可能在以色列袭击中丧生 ■ 战争开始 126 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 17:25:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-126/0000018d-8ea2-d57f-a1ef-bebebf870000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的另一场“全面胜利”可能已经到来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-other-total-victory-may-already-be-here/0000018d-8e4a-d9cc-a5cd-fffa27750000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 16:03:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahus-other-total-victory-may-already-be-here/0000018d-8e4a-d9cc-a5cd-fffa27750000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡命令以色列军队提出撤离拉法平民、击败哈马斯的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-orders-israeli-army-to-present-plans-to-evacuate-rafah-civilians-defeat-hamas/0000018d-8e6e-d7bc-a7fd-afef6a250000</link><description>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡表示，“在拉法留下四个哈马斯营是不可能实现消灭哈马斯的战争目标的”</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 15:59:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-orders-israeli-army-to-present-plans-to-evacuate-rafah-civilians-defeat-hamas/0000018d-8e6e-d7bc-a7fd-afef6a250000</guid></item><item><title>美国对加沙战争的政策如何导致以色列、美国和阿拉伯世界的意见两极分化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/how-u-s-policy-on-gaza-war-has-polarized-opinion-in-israel-america-and-the-arab-world/0000018d-8e52-d443-a19f-fed3458b0000</link><description>仁慈的拜登与坏人的拜登：随着时间的推移，美国总统可能会将全球主要选民推入怨恨阵营，而且这种情况可能是无法挽回的</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 15:57:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/how-u-s-policy-on-gaza-war-has-polarized-opinion-in-israel-america-and-the-arab-world/0000018d-8e52-d443-a19f-fed3458b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军调查发现人质很可能在空军轰炸中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-investigation-reveals-high-probability-that-hostage-killed-during-air-force-bombing/0000018d-8e4d-d9cc-a5cd-ffffe7840000</link><description>以色列军队认为，约西·沙拉比在以色列国防军对他和另外两名人质被关押的地方附近的一栋建筑进行袭击时被杀</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 15:02:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-investigation-reveals-high-probability-that-hostage-killed-during-air-force-bombing/0000018d-8e4d-d9cc-a5cd-ffffe7840000</guid></item><item><title>战时以色列的愤怒正在上升，以色列人必须去战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/anger-is-rising-in-wartime-israel-about-which-israelis-must-go-and-fight/0000018d-89a7-d9cc-a5cd-fdbf2eb20000</link><description>自加沙战争开始以来，许多预备役军人已经穿了四个月的军装，以色列的极端正统派和世俗社区正在就谁必须在以色列国防军服役的问题发生冲突。总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡已经在努力集结军队</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 14:33:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/anger-is-rising-in-wartime-israel-about-which-israelis-must-go-and-fight/0000018d-89a7-d9cc-a5cd-fdbf2eb20000</guid></item><item><title>联合国表示，加沙近 10% 的五岁以下儿童现在严重营养不良</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/almost-10-percent-of-gazas-under-fives-now-acutely-malnourished-un-says/0000018d-8e04-d1e0-a3ff-9ffff73a0000</link><description>由于食品卡车经常遭到饥饿人群的围攻，救援人员报告说，儿童有明显的饥饿迹象，特别是在加沙北部和中部地区</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 13:57:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/almost-10-percent-of-gazas-under-fives-now-acutely-malnourished-un-says/0000018d-8e04-d1e0-a3ff-9ffff73a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空袭加沙拉法，美国警告不要在该市进行地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/israeli-airstrikes-hit-gazas-rafah-as-u-s-warns-against-ground-operation-in-city/0000018d-8d83-d9cc-a5cd-fdbb03d70000</link><description>连夜空袭造成 22 人死亡，袭击了拉法的两栋住宅楼，并损坏了一座由幼儿园改建的流离失所巴勒斯坦人避难所</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 11:47:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/israeli-airstrikes-hit-gazas-rafah-as-u-s-warns-against-ground-operation-in-city/0000018d-8d83-d9cc-a5cd-fdbb03d70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登称以色列在加沙的反应“过度”，寻求暂停战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/biden-israeli-military-conduct-in-gaza-over-the-top-working-for-sustained-pause/0000018d-8c88-d5e7-ad8d-efa867620000</link><description>拜登表示，他一直与卡塔尔、埃及和沙特阿拉伯领导人保持联系，以使最大程度的人道主义援助进入加沙。总统补充说，“有很多无辜的人正在挨饿、陷入困境和死亡”。 “它必须停止”</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 06:42:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/biden-israeli-military-conduct-in-gaza-over-the-top-working-for-sustained-pause/0000018d-8c88-d5e7-ad8d-efa867620000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡向以色列人发出明确信息：放弃人质符合国家利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-clear-message-to-israelis-abandoning-the-hostages-is-in-the-national-interest/0000018d-8a8b-d443-a19f-fe9baf840000</link><description>总理“全面胜利”口号的潜台词是，以人质换取停火协议将阻止以色列国防军完成任务。 与此同时，领土政府活动协调员正准备重新实施戒严令关于加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 04:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-clear-message-to-israelis-abandoning-the-hostages-is-in-the-national-interest/0000018d-8a8b-d443-a19f-fe9baf840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的协议尚未结束，即使内塔尼亚胡另有说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-deal-is-not-dead-yet-even-if-netanyahu-says-otherwise/0000018d-898c-d9cc-a5cd-fdbe698c0000</link><description>与总理给人的印象相反，哈马斯的回答似乎为达成协议留下了回旋余地。 ■ 战争期间的战术成就并不能保证以色列取得“全面”战略胜利。 ■ 服务负担正在扩大，但并没有增加。对于极端正统派</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-deal-is-not-dead-yet-even-if-netanyahu-says-otherwise/0000018d-898c-d9cc-a5cd-fdbe698c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡命令以色列军队提出撤离拉法平民、击败哈马斯的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-live/biden-says-israeli-military-conduct-in-gaza-is-over-the-top-pushing-for-pause/0000018d-8be5-d5e7-ad8d-ebe5fc430000</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡要求以色列国防军制定双重计划，从拉法撤离平民并击败哈马斯部队 ■ 从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射反坦克导弹，以色列空军发起报复性打击 ■ 叙利亚称在大马士革附近击落了两架无人机 ■ 匈牙利、捷克共和国沉没欧盟努力对暴力的以色列定居者实施制裁</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 03:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-live/biden-says-israeli-military-conduct-in-gaza-is-over-the-top-pushing-for-pause/0000018d-8be5-d5e7-ad8d-ebe5fc430000</guid></item></channel></rss>